Rakes
Rakes are picks with a serrated or wavy profile designed to be moved in and out
|
:INFO
Rakes
Rakes are picks with a serrated or wavy profile designed to be moved in and out under \
tension to set multiple pins simultaneously. The city rake (also called an S-rake) and \
the snake rake are the two most useful starting points. Raking is fast on cheap

